    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-80f9-8864-fa9ec36204e8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Study wants to study factors that promote group engagement and teamwork by measuring how cultural diversity, trust and group formation affect team performance. Data is samples from a Questionnaire and uses SEM to identify the most likely predictors of of behavioral and cognitive engagement.",
